title: All-Flash Quarterly (001 - 005) & All Flash (006 - 032) (194
description:
All-Flash Quarterly (001 - 005) & All Flash (006 - 032) (1941 - 1948)


In 1940, writer Gardner Fox and artist Harry Lampert created the Flash. Jay Garrick made his debut in Flash Comics #1.The series featured the Flash, Hawkman, and a rotating cast of other heroes.
. The Flash proved so popular he gained a series of his own, All-Flash Quarterly in 1941 (soon shortened to just All-Flash)
